messages.message:
Listing down the issues, I have inferred from the above message

• Model response getting truncated - Since the underlying model used was different we are seeing the differences in the response. For query #2, advanced model was used and query #3, multistep model was used. So that's the different
• Bounding box based provenance - this feature is supported only for advanced models (single document query). With multistep model and multi document queries we support only page level provenance
• Steps shows all the intermediate steps executed by the model to arrive at an answer. Are you concerned that we are showing the failure message in the intermediate steps?
